a, mandarin and almond cake","publishedAt":"2014-07-22T00:00:00Z","nutrition":{"protein":"7.4 g","fat":"32.3 g","uom":"per 1 portion","carbohydrates":"31.8 g","calories":"1865 kJ \/ 444 kcal"},"usefulItems":"baking paper, round springform cake tin (22 cm), baking paper, wooden skewer, oven","hintsAndTricks":["To ensure gluten free recipes are gluten free, always read the labels of your products to ensure no wheat or gluten has been used as part of the production process."],"basicInfo":["easy","10m","2h 35m","12 portions"]}